{"tid":2142522,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蛇姬林采緹出海靚相驚現超大碼腳掌　網民嚇親：真的是NBA足","createTime":"2020-08-06T12:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T15:55:40.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"906e1c997b4120468f76a325c4cd7dd1c37ca13a","tid":2142522,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T12:48:48.000Z","msg":"台灣性感女藝人林采緹當年憑住cosplay漫畫《海賊王》入面的女帝蛇姬而出名，她的索爆身材完美演繹出蛇姬的誘人魅力，令人印象難忘。現在的她雖然已為人母，亦很久都沒有再扮蛇姬了，不過做了媽咪的她，身材依然keep得好好，同擁有S形迷人Body shape的蛇姬沒兩樣，絕對是一個辣媽。<br />\n<br />\n她亦經常於IG post新相來update她的近況，同大家分享她的生活點滴。日前她post了幾張出海遊船河的靚相，卻被網民發現赤腳的她腳掌異常地大隻，甚至和NBA球員的腳掌大小不相上下，與她的高度和身形不太合比例。有網民指她的腳掌比一般人要大出3分之1，惹來熱烈的討論，有網民就留言表示：「真的是NBA足」。"},{"pid":"821de4b63557cdf4ad4735ee7c6488d3df643415","tid":2142522,"uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T12:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200623/352175226563465217.jpeg/gWL6A2PfXlO7mWYZHLt9IOLfdFV4pk2BGFc1txhXNbc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200623%2F352175226563465217.jpeg%2FgWL6A2PfXlO7mWYZHLt9IOLfdFV4pk2BGFc1txhXNbc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=af0e2558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200806/368056986715164672.jpeg/EWv4u0jH5ftakPoKXV6YZeJibzsVUAikYo7jdmKO43Y?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200806%2F368056986715164672.jpeg%2FEWv4u0jH5ftakPoKXV6YZeJibzsVUAikYo7jdmKO43Y%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=a2f96a8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200806/368056989043003392.jpeg/iBE9LjxU_-UP4sMEDY1OkU1Yv9Elf5UueGOO83hjjvM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200806%2F368056989043003392.jpeg%2FiBE9LjxU_-UP4sMEDY1OkU1Yv9Elf5UueGOO83hjjvM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=72bfcbac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di